summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting from the State of Washington a Governor's Deed conveying to the City of Seattle portions of the West one-half of Section 32, Township 25 North, Range 4 East, of the Willamette Meridian, for General Municipal Park, and Street purposes, and laying off University Street, 8th Avenue, Union Street, 9th Avenue, Hubbell Place, Pike Street, Boren Avenue, Terry Avenue, Seneca Street, Spring Street and 7th Avenue.
